description:
Rattan Outdoor Furniture’s Bringhton outdoor patio chaise lounge brings ultimate luxury and incredible durability with this one-of-a-kind uniquely fashioned outdoor patio chaise lounge. Our Bringhton collection features all-weather, powder-coated alumunium framing covered in Rehau, a UV-resistant and weather-resistant resin wicker. See how beautiful our high-resilience (HR) ultra-plush cushioning wrapped in Allure fabric feels, resisting color fading and seasonal mildew to keep your outdoor patio chaise lounge looking like new for years to come.

  • Product Overview
  • Dimensions:186 x 68 x 58
  • Features: Adjustable back, hand-woven
  • Cushion material: Polyester fiber; 100%
  • Allure fabric is made out of Olefin 100%, UV and mildew-resistant
  • Reversible zippered cushions with contrasting welting
  • Rehau woven wicker on rust-proof alumunium frame
  • 1-year limited manufacturer warranty
  • Weight capacity: 250.0 Lbs
  • Imported
